<?xml version="1.0"?><speak version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis" xml:lang="zh-CN"><prosody rate="slow" pitch="high"><emphasis level="strong">《月光酿成的乡愁》</emphasis></prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">各位朋友，<break strength="medium"/>让我们回到一千三百年前的扬州客栈。<break strength="medium"/>深秋的霜风掠过雕花木窗，<break strength="medium"/>惊醒了一位辗转反侧的诗人。<break strength="medium"/>他便是刚过而立之年的李白，<break strength="medium"/>此刻正经历着唐代文人必经的漫游生涯。<break strength="medium"/>且听这四句清辉，<break strength="medium"/>如何凝成千古绝唱——（朗诵，<break strength="medium"/>语速徐缓，<break strength="medium"/>重音落在&quot;明月&quot;&quot;故乡&quot;）</prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">床前明月光，<break strength="medium"/>疑是地上霜。<break strength="medium"/>举头望明月，<break strength="medium"/>低头思故乡。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">（停顿三秒，<break strength="medium"/>转为温润的讲述）这二十个字里藏着多少游子的心事啊。<break strength="medium"/>诗人将月光比作白霜，<break strength="medium"/>不仅是视觉的错觉，<break strength="medium"/>更是心底泛起的寒凉。<break strength="medium"/>抬头与低首之间，<break strength="medium"/>目光从浩渺苍穹转向方寸心田，<break strength="medium"/>完成了天地与故园的深情对话。<break strength="medium"/>盛唐的月光穿越驿道山水，<break strength="medium"/>此刻正静静流淌在异乡的床榻前。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">（音调渐柔，<break strength="medium"/>如月光流淌）那个秋夜，<break strength="medium"/>青衫上还沾着长安的酒痕，<break strength="medium"/>案头未干的墨迹写着《蜀道难》的狂放。<break strength="medium"/>可当月光漫过窗棂，<break strength="medium"/>所有豪情都化作了绕指柔。<break strength="medium"/>他恍惚看见童年庭院里，<break strength="medium"/>母亲也是这样清冷的月光下教他辨认星斗；父亲远行时，<break strength="medium"/>那袭白袍也似这般被月色浸透。<break strength="medium"/>忽然响起的更鼓惊碎幻影，<break strength="medium"/>才发觉手中握着的，<break strength="medium"/>是白日里收到的家书——信纸折痕处，<break strength="medium"/>还留着阿妹采撷的桂花。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="strong"/><prosody rate="slow" pitch="medium">（语速渐缓，<break strength="medium"/>尾音绵长）千年后的我们依然在这轮明月下驻足，<break strength="medium"/>因为每个华夏儿女的血液里，<break strength="medium"/>都流淌着&quot;举头望明月&quot;的基因。<break strength="medium"/>李太白用二十个最简单的文字，<break strength="medium"/>凿穿了时空的壁垒，<break strength="medium"/>让所有离乡的游子，<break strength="medium"/>都能在月光里打捞属于自己的乡愁。<break strength="medium"/>此刻，<break strength="medium"/>且让这四行诗句化作一叶扁舟，<break strength="medium"/>载着我们穿越浩荡星河，<break strength="medium"/>回到心灵的原乡。<break strength="medium"/></prosody><break strength="strong"/></speak>